A Davis townie. One of the founders of the Davis Music Scene. A good portion of the debt is owed to this man for his contributions to DMS. He played sporatically with a number of bands that he wrote nearly all the material for, including: False Dawn, Shots Were Fired and Carl and Company. The core of most of these bands consisted of Carl, Alex Stupakov, and Users/AndrewMatey. Carl currently resides in wiki:santacruz Santa Cruz.
